Dotfiles
--------
My dotfiles might be a little bit messy. I'm just storing them here so it's easier for me to download them.
Since people might find it's somewhat useful, I decided to make it a public repo. 

Basic info
----------
OS: Arch Linux (vanilla kernel)
Display Server: Wayland
Window manager: sway
Filesystem: btrfs
Display manager: None (autostart with fish)
Audio: Pipewire (alsa & pulse)

System
------
Bar: waybar
Menu: wofi
Screenshots: swappy
Wallpaper: wallpaper.jpg

Software
--------
Shell: fish
Reader: zathura
Image Viewer: sxiv
Media player: mpv
Music: Spotify 
Terminal: alacritty
Telegram: Kotatogram
Torrent: QBittorrent
Browser: Firefox 
VM: virt-manager (QEMU + KVM)
IDE: PyCharm, Intellij, Doom Emacs (not here yet)

Appearance 
----------
GTK Theme: Breeze
Colorscheme: Nord
Spotify theme: Dribblish
Firefox theme: Simplerent Fox
Fonts: JetBrains Mono NF, Meslo NF, SF Pro
